            "correct_answer": "Different sounds",
            "explanation": "Same vowel mark, but different commanders ‚Üí different sounds.\nSun consonant (·ûÄ) ‚Üí sound stays clear/light (kaa)\nMoon consonant (·ûÇ) ‚Üí sound changes, gets 'colored' by the deep tone (kea)"
          }
        },
        {
